### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Xeno Mini CRM — API Test Requests
### Open in VS Code with REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 2. Win-back lapsed customers
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I want to win back customers who used to buy regularly but stopped in the last 3 months"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 3. Target champions (recent + frequent + high-value)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Show me my best customers — loyal, recent buyers who spend a lot"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4. Find new customers to nurture
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Find customers who bought for the first time in the last month"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 5. At-risk dormant segment
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Customers who haven't purchased in over 90 days and only bought once or twice"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 6. Mid-value cooling off
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I want customers who bought 60 days ago but not in last 30"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 7. Big spenders across all time
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Show me customers who have spent more than 15000 rupees total"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 8. Frequent buyers with low spend (upsell opportunity)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Find frequent buyers who have placed 5+ orders but spent less than 8000 total — I want to upsell them"
}

