### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### PHASE 1c: Campaign Send (/api/campaigns)
### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###
### ⚠️  NOTE: customer_ids must be real UUIDs from your DB.
### Get some with: SELECT id FROM customers LIMIT 5;
### Replace the placeholder UUIDs below with real ones.
###

### 13. Send campaign — Lapsed High-Value Win-back
POST http://localhost:3000/api/campaigns/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "segment_name": "Lapsed High-Value Shoppers",
  "persona": "Lapsed High-Value",
  "message": "Hey! Winter collection is almost sold out. Remember those jackets you loved? Shop now before they're gone → [link]",
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "tone": "Urgent",
  "estimated_open_rate": "48%",
  "customer_ids": [
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003"
  ]
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 14. Send campaign — Champions VIP Offer
POST http://localhost:3000/api/campaigns/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "segment_name": "Champions - VIP Loyal",
  "persona": "Champions",
  "message": "VIP Offer: 25% off our new winter collection. This exclusive deal is just for our best customers. Claim offer in 24hrs → [link]",
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "tone": "Value",
  "estimated_open_rate": "55%",
  "customer_ids": [
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004",
    "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005"
  ]
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 15. Validation error — missing required fields
POST http://localhost:3000/api/campaigns/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "segment_name": "Test",
  "message": "Hello!"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 16. Get campaign stats (replace :id with a real campaign UUID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/campaigns/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/stats

### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### PHASE 1d: Channel Service (localhost:5001)
### Start with: npm run channel
### ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 17. Channel Service health check
GET http://localhost:5001/health

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 18. Simulate delivery for 3 messages
### Watch the main CRM terminal for webhook callbacks arriving!
POST http://localhost:5001/simulate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campaign_id": "test-campaign-001",
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "callback_url": "http://localhost:3000/api/webhooks/channel-events",
  "messages": [
    {
      "customer_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
      "phone": "+91-9876543210",
      "message": "Hey! Winter collection is almost sold out. Shop now →",
      "channel": "whatsapp"
    },
    {
      "customer_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
      "phone": "+91-8765432109",
      "message": "Hey! Winter collection is almost sold out. Shop now →",
      "channel": "whatsapp"
    },
    {
      "customer_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
      "phone": "+91-7654321098",
      "message": "Hey! Winter collection is almost sold out. Shop now →",
      "channel": "whatsapp"
    }
  ]
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 19. Manual webhook test (simulate a callback to main CRM)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/webhooks/channel-events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "campaign_id": "test-campaign-001",
  "customer_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "phone": "+91-9876543210",
  "event_type": "delivered",
  "timestamp": "2026-06-10T14:22:35Z"
}
